<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Room Reservation Accepted</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 20px;">
        <h2 style="color: #333;">Room Reservation Accepted for Syphax Hotel</h2>
        <p>Dear {{ userName }},</p>
        <p>Congratulations! Your reservation request for the following room at Syphax Hotel has been accepted:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Room: {{ roomName }}</li>
            <li>Floor Number: {{ floorNumber }}</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We are pleased to confirm your reservation. Please proceed with the necessary steps to finalize the booking and make any required arrangements.</p>
        <p>Thank you for choosing {{ hotelName }}!</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
